&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gr.gvp6nx1a.duckdns.org/d/fdyt7rjk3owzkd/med-exam?orgId=1"&gt;바로 가기 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://agknwpt3.grafana.net/d/fdyt7rjk3owzkd/med-exam?orgId=1&amp;amp;from=2024-07-23T15:00:00.000Z&amp;amp;to=2024-09-09T14:59:59.000Z&amp;amp;timezone=Asia%2FSeoul&amp;amp;var-usr_id=9VFsW2u8mIqFXMlG7f6irg%3D%3D&amp;amp;var-exam_type_cd=002&amp;amp;var-exam_id=RT51KR-PK01&amp;amp;var-rslt_ymd=$__all&amp;amp;var-exam_a_gb_cd=$__all&amp;amp;var-grdng_cd=$__all&amp;amp;var-exam_b_gb_cd=$__all&amp;amp;var-ai_model=$__all"&gt;바로 가기 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
